001package io.ebean.cache;
002
003/**
004 * The type of L2 caches.
005 */
006public enum ServerCacheType {
007
008  /**
009   * Bean cache.
010   */
011  BEAN("_B"),
012
013  /**
014   * Natural key cache.
015   */
016  NATURAL_KEY("_N"),
017
018  /**
019   * Collection Ids for Many properties.
020   */
021  COLLECTION_IDS("_C"),
022
023  /**
024   * Query cache.
025   */
026  QUERY("_Q");
027
028  private String code;
029
030  ServerCacheType(String code) {
031    this.code = code;
032  }
033
034  public String code(){
035    return code;
036  }
037}
